                    </li>
                  </ul>
                  <span class="gend-link"></span>
                </li>
                <li>
                  » <strong>pride and prejudice</strong> «
                  <em>jane austen</em> (1813)
                  <ul>
                    <li>
                      (great love story but too many plot lines i don't care
                      about, and too long) <span class="gend-link"></span>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                  <span class="gend-link"></span>
                </li>
                <li>
                  » <strong>sherlock holmes</strong> «
                  <em>arthur conan doyle</em> (1887)
                  <ul>
                    <li>
