                    </li>
                  </ul>
                  <span class="gend-link"></span>
                </li>
                <li>
                  » <strong>the picture of dorian gray</strong> «
                  <em>oscar wilde</em> (1890)
                  <ul>
                    <li>
                      (i loved this. great main characters (very gay), just one
                      plot line i didn't care about)
                      <span class="gend-link"></span>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                  <span class="gend-link"></span>
                </li>
