                    </li>
                  </ul>
                  <span class="gend-link"></span>
                </li>
                <li>
                  » <strong>dr. jekyll and mr. hyde</strong> «
                  <em>robert louis stevenson</em> (1886)
                  <ul>
                    <li>
                      (short and sweet, i love the vibes)
